Description.LocalizedString: Reveals the auras of both Killers when they perform the break action on pallets, generators, or breakable walls.
Reveals the aura of injured Survivors within 128 meters.
Increases healing speed by 35%.

Gain 3% Haste while injured.

Haste increases Survivor movement speed.

While in a chainsaw sprint, Survivors within 10 meters suffer from the Exposed status effect until the chainsaw sprint ends.

Exposed Survivors will be downed by basic attacks even if uninjured.

Injuring a Survivor with a hatchet inflicts the Revealed status effect for 5 seconds.

Revealed shows the Survivor's aura to both Killers.
While a Killer is within line of sight within 64 meters, their aura is revealed to the team.
When repairing a generator, reveals your aura and your generator's aura to your team.
Reveals the auras of any generators within 16 meters.

While healing another Survivor, their aura is revealed to the team.

Survivors within 3 meters gain a 25% bonus when healing others.

This does not apply while in a chase.

While sprinting, all Survivors within 12 meters gain 150% Haste for 3 seconds. This Team Skill has a cooldown of 20 seconds.

Haste increases Survivor movement speed.

When a Bear Trap is placed or reset, both Killers gain 150% Haste for 3 seconds within 16 meters of the Bear Trap.

Haste increases Killer movement speed.

Grunts of pain caused by injuries are reduced while crouching.

Increases movement speed while crouching.
Reveals the auras of pallets, windows, and breakable walls within 32 meters.

While cloaked within 16 meters of your teammate, they gain the Undetectable status effect.

Undetectablehides the Killer's aura,Terror Radius,and Red Stain.

Start the trial with 3 additional hatchets.

Increases movement speed by 4.5% when out of hatchets.

Decreases reload time by 20%.

Decreases cooldown between hatchet throws by 20%.

Increases movement speed during wind-up by 5%.

The Trapper cannot be caught in his Bear Traps.

Increases Bear Trap setting speed by 50% and increases the time required to escape a Bear Trap by 25%.

Start with 4 Traps. Increases the maximum number of carried Traps to 4.

8 Traps spawn in the map.

Increases cloaking and uncloaking speed by 22%.

Increases movement speed while cloaked by 9%.

Increases Chainsaw Sprint turn speed by 44%.

Decreases cooldown after hitting obstacles by 12%.

Chainsaw does not automatically trigger dying state.
Gain an additional Blink while within 16 meters of your teammate. This additional Blink is lost when out of range.

Increases the length of Blink Attack lunges by 30%.

Increases reach by 30% with each consecutive Blink.

Decreases the duration of Blink fatigue by 7%.

Teleporting within 1 meter of a Survivor causes them to scream.

Decreases fatigue from Chain Blinks by 65%.

Increases movement speed during a chain Blink by 30%.

Increases the duration of the chain Blink window by 0.2 seconds.

Decreases fatigue from missing Special Attacks by 0.5 seconds.

After reaching the second cage state, Survivors gain the ability to self-heal and fully recover. Once a Survivor has fully recovered themselves, having completed at least 25% of their own recovery progression, they gain the Endurance status effect for 20 seconds and a 10% Haste status effect for 10 seconds.

Endurance prevents a Survivor from being downed, inflicting Deep Wound instead.

Upon entering a chase, the targeted Survivors are Revealed for 5 seconds, or until the other Killer is within 16 meters of the Survivor.

Revealed shows the Survivor's aura to both Killers.

After kicking a generator, all Survivors within 20 meters are Revealed for 5 seconds.

Increases the regression speed of generators by 200%.

Revealed shows the Survivor's aura to both Killers.

Survivors within 8 meters gain an additional 3% bonus progress for great Skill Checks while repairing generators, and the noises caused by your repairs are reduced by 50%.

This does not apply when the Survivor is hiding in a locker.
